Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.04,0:01:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.74,0:01:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關於5月1日的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.24,0:01:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那天下午可以出去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀 那天正好沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？要和小花他們出去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 那天是母親的忌日 想去掃墓一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 都一周年忌了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.96,0:01:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但也沒有特別準備什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 沒辦法一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以一起去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想掃掃妳母親的墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我媽媽一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.75,0:02:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天如果沒事的話 你也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.59,0:02:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那王子也要去囉 阿夾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 他什麼都沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日子應該會喜歡阿夾他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以跟他們打成一片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橘子 橘子 我要吃了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.60,0:02:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於將快要無法忍受的阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.88,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從背後一副餓虎撲羊的態勢緊緊的抱住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊 代志大條哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳母親過世…已經一年了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在仍覺得哪天她會突然跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.43,0:03:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邊笑著邊說"不好意思 不好意思"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 氣氛搞的有點冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也表示今日子很了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像"環七紅蝴蝶"傳說般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雄偉的"裝飾卡車"讓人一輩子都忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾卡車指的就是額頭凸出的卡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.69,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亂講！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能去掃墓就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我也要去掃墓喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛跟我說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆 我說要去就要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在畫什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好小的一間廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.17,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡隨意的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對廟這麼講究幹什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好天氣變好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近老是陰晴不定 我還有點擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能媽媽也很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.22,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們大家都來了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是掃墓的好日子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼裝扮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說"什麼"是啥意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然太樸素了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陰了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚谷…莫非這是特攻隊的衣服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你很內行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是今日子給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正統紅蝶特攻隊隊長穿的衣服唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅蝶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我媽當年的藝名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藝名？還笑得那麼開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦！該到的都到了 我們快出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很興奮 超興奮的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？很乾淨耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來過了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為爺爺清楚媽媽喜歡吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那位老伯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位爺爺是哪一邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟今日子那邊的父母就比較疏遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你父親又為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說因為感冒就這麼走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還小不太記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽 我們來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺都整理過了 好像沒什麼可做的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.14,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親走了 母親也去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透為何能那麼開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是笑顏洋溢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外當天的事我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上課中她突然被老師叫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談了一陣後…就飛奔而去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位朋友也緊追在後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教室頓然一陣騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.27,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還在想是不是她的家人遭到什麼意外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那件事情 我只是淡淡的猜想了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對當時的本田透這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有這樣淡淡的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在卻同住一個屋簷下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此的親近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己能夠這樣子跟她一同歡笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來很好吃呢 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在墓地野餐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱鬧一點今日子也會很開心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被廟裡的人發現了怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道歉就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是一般是不會這樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之別嘮嘮叨叨的 快坐下來吧 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣站著讓人很不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 要吃點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.85,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚谷妳們跟小透的媽媽很熟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很照顧我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認識以前就是傳說中的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很崇拜她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說人物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是紅蝶傳說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼傳說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日子一騎上摩托車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像蝴蝶起舞般 後面的尾燈閃爍個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會聽不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個也很好吃\N你也真沒想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這個也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你別講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過一年後的現在可以這樣開懷的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.91,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那段期間一定斥責過無數次軟弱的自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果換成我失去了重要的親人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒把握一年後是否可以這樣的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如要是小透死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會因為太痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而甚至想要忘掉曾與她交往的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但小透她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻那麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想…不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也多虧他們兩人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們三個之間的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近愈來愈好不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知哪天誰會先說出喜歡小透的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會那麼輕易的承認他們的交往呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是小透的婆婆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是半開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有一半是真的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩由希還有草摩夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.66,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎依舊無法跳脫出心中的那塊陰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事每個人多少都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是他們兩人算是嚴重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要那個怨恨還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們大概沒有談戀愛的心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還想強調一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆對這種事又特別遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點小透也一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時也會在莫名其妙中突然開花結果的情況呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我才不要小透嫁出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光想就想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦一天之後的茶是最香的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的掃墓真愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.94,0:11:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興終於能把由希與阿夾介紹給媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.65,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人很照顧我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪天要是能再介紹紫吳給妳認識就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽 我住在這裡 每天都和大家過得很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以請妳放心 繼續保佑我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是謝謝你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 反倒吃了妳一頓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳的下廚功夫愈來愈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳隨時可以嫁人去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拋下我一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們正在玩警察捉小偷的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 你再躲也沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 被發現了 我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看前面呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現紅葉了 快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是精力旺盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看前面呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼看都像男生在追女生似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該比較像媽媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人家不是常說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生像媽媽 女生像爸爸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起媽媽 小透也比較像爸爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是像爺爺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 紅葉的父母好像也沒來參加開學典禮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一位白髮的男生也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.04,0:13:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家的人好像都絕口不提他們的父母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很重呢 我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟大廈是爸爸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你爸爸在這裡工作嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 但是…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說 爸爸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡呀 剛剛老闆一直再找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你轉告爸爸 我要回去了請他不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爺？老闆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸的第12棟大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這個意思呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有照片喔 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父親好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫柔好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢…爸爸是草摩的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是在大學時認識媽媽才結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好厲害居然能娶到媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 我還有個妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫小桃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桃和媽媽長得很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也有其他兄弟姊妹呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她今年小學2年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但小桃不是十二生肖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴妳她和媽媽好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還很會撒嬌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟屁蟲般 老是黏在媽媽身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她不太會講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.19,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌頭不太靈光但真的很可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講得興高采烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和小桃都會來接爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大概快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就可以一起回家了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 能那樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但媽媽不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 這時間你在這裡幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操 曹操就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:16:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這位就是小桃囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但紅葉還是比較像媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友在這裡打工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來找她玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀 但這裡不是玩耍的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太晚回去的話你媽媽也會擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我現在就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那要直接回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桃 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸可能等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真倒楣 被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下得向爸爸自首才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她因為記憶移除 已經忘了我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.81,0:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一直以為我是草摩家某人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被怪物附身的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.95,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比10月10日預產期早兩個月出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇見喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和喜歡的人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.56,0:17:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並生下對方的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果擁抱那個孩子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成奇怪的動物寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對媽媽而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是多麼的絕望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生下被怪物附身的小孩的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是變得太過於保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是受到萬分驚嚇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我媽媽就是受到萬分驚嚇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身受到驚嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡量不看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但儘管如此 她還是很焦慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是歇斯底里的大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是崩潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像佳菜那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.64,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也許無可救藥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果忘了你的事或許可以治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.25,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.19,0:18:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸會連媽媽的份加倍愛你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.39,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉如果也愛媽媽就救救媽媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.93,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的要忘掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會後悔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子最後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是生下那怪胎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從媽媽的記憶中消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽恢復得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月後就會笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣做 不知道對媽媽有沒有幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來他一直暗地裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從遠方小心翼翼地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不被發現地守護著媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.59,0:19:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想珍惜這份回憶勇敢的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是一個令人哀傷的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個讓我痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是一個讓我想忘掉的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要面對它 不逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信有一天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我會成為能夠勝過這份回憶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼深信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想這麼相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.16,0:20:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望沒有任何一個回憶是可以遺忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不希望媽媽忘了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不可以太任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是何種回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要深藏心裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且深信著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.98,0:21:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望沒有任何一個回憶是可以遺忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.96,0:21:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天一定會成為能夠勝過這些的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且總有一天能夠超越這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為美好的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信著
